snippet.textDisplay:
TRANSLATION | SUBTITLE

Ae Rah-e-Haq Ke Shaheedo =  O, the Martyrs of the Right Path
Wafa ki taswero = Depiction of faithfulness
Tumhe watan ki hawayen salam kehti hain = Breeze of this country salutes you
Ae Rah-e-Haq Ke Shaheedo =  O, the Martyrs of the Right Path

ALLAH HOOO

Lagane Aag Jo Aye The Ashyane Ko  = Those who came to burn aerie
Woh Sholey Apne Lahoo Se Bujhadiye Tumnee  = You put off those flames with your blood.
Bachalaiya Hai yateemi se Kitne Pholon Ko = You saved so many flowers (kids) from orphanhood 
Suhag Kitni Baharon K Rakh Liye Tumnee = You saved so many springs (married females) from being widowed
Tumhe Chaman Ki Fazain Salam Kheti Hain  = Skies of this garden salutes you 
Ae Rah-e-Haq Ke Shaheedo =  O, the Martyrs of the Right Path

Chale Jo Hoge Shahadat Ka Jaam Piker Tum = You went away after tasting martyrdom
Rasool-e-pak Ne Banhoon Main Leliya Hoga  = Prophet (P.B.U.H) must have embraced you in his arms.
Ali Tumhari Shuja\'at Pay Jhomte Honge  = Ali (A.S) must be proud of you bravery
Husain Pak Ne Irshad Yeh Kya Hoga = Hussain (A.S) must have said
Tumnhe Khuda Ki Razain Salam Kehti Hain = Lord's pleasures salute you
Ae Rah-e-Haq Ke Shaheedo =  O, the Martyrs of the Right Path
